'''Google云端推送'''（{{lang-en|'''G'''oogle '''C'''loud '''M'''essaging}}，简称'''{{lang|en|GCM}}'''）是一項免費服务，帮助开发者从[[服务器|服务器]]发送数据到安装了他们的应用程序的[[Android|Android]]设备上，或从服务器到其[[Google_Chrome|Chrome浏览器]]应用程序或扩展。<ref name="GCM Android 開發人員說明">{{Cite web |url = https://support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/answer/2663268?hl=zh-Hant |title = Google雲端通訊 (GCM) - Android 開發人員說明 |publisher = Google |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2014-11-12 |quote =  |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141112005242/https://support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/answer/2663268?hl=zh-Hant |archivedate = 2014-11-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="GCM Android Developer帮助">{{Cite web |url = https://support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/answer/2663268?hl=zh-Hans |title = Google云消息传递(GCM) - Android Developer帮助 |publisher = Google |language = zh-hans |accessdate = 2014-11-12 |quote =  |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141112010425/https://support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/answer/2663268?hl=zh-Hans |archivedate = 2014-11-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>Android云端推送服务第一次亮相是在2012年6月27日在[[旧金山|旧金山]]Moscone中心举行的[[Google_I/O|Google I/O 2012]]。<ref name = "Google’s New Cloud Messaging System Does More for Less – Gizmodo">{{cite web
